data.description: Come see this great home located in Mesa school district!  Walk into the home and feel invited into the roomy living room with beautiful fireplace.  You'll love the open concept with eat in kitchen that overlooks the living room. The master suite is complete with an en suite master bathroom that includes a jetted tub, separate shower, double sink vanity and HUGE, walk in closet.  You don't want to miss this one! Schedule your viewing today!
